= Mixture-of-Superpositions-based Verification Protocol <ch:mos>

The goal of Caro, Hinsche, Ioannou, Nieter, and Sweke @Caro_2023 was to discover a way of recovering
the Fourier spectrum of a Boolean parity function in the distributional-agnostic setting, and verify
its heaviest coefficients with only a classical verifier. They acieved this using their novel
Mixture-of-Superpositions technique.

